common.graph

Class AbstractVertex<T extends AbstractEdge<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.CObject
      • common.graph.AbstractVertex<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the AbstractEdge
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HyperVertexTemplate, VertexTemplate

    public abstract class AbstractVertex<T extends AbstractEdge<?>>
extends CObject
    The AbstractVertex class is a class representing the node(s) of a AbstractGraph.
    Author:
    Vincent Mirian
    Date:
    Nov 15, 2017
